metadata.name: April
metadata.description:
Hello, I'm in43.
I went to see cherry blossoms to welcome spring again this year.
April is my favorite month because it has my birthday and spring begins.
I want you to feel this spring coming up with my work.

She is Natsuha Seto.
Although she was born in summer, she has a sweet personality like spring.
She is the best friend to greet spring together among my OCs.
